Introduction

Ollie is a Chinese trainee under Yuehua Entertainment. He was one of the contestants of the 2022 survival show "Boys Planet." He competed on "Asia Super Young" with his final rank being 1st, meaning he will debut as a member of a China/Hong Kong based group called LOONG9.
